T*
(Because on the phone, `127.0.0.1` means the phone itself, not the laptop.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(For mobile testing on the same Wi-Fi, use the laptop's local IP address and run Laravel like) Tj
T*
(this:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(```bash) Tj
T*
(php artisan serve --host=0.0.0.0 --port=8001) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Then the mobile link may look like:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(```txt) Tj
T*
