T*
(Backend Flow) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(When a user creates a short link:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(```txt) Tj
T*
(React frontend) Tj
T*
(-> POST /api/urls) Tj
T*
(-> Laravel UrlController) Tj
T*
(-> ShortCodeGenerator creates 8-character code) Tj
T*
(-> Save original URL and short code in database) Tj
T*
(-> Return short URL to frontend) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(When someone opens a short link:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(```txt) Tj
T*
(Browser opens /J7qudkrM) Tj
T*
(-> Laravel RedirectController) Tj
T*
(-> Find short code in cache or database) Tj
T*
(-> Dispatch click tracking job) Tj
T*
(-> Redirect user to original URL) Tj
T*
(```) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Database Tables) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The `urls` table stores:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Original long URL) Tj
T*
(- Short code) Tj
T*
(- Click count) Tj
T*
(- Active or paused status) Tj
T*
(- Expiry date) Tj
T*
(- Last clicked time) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
ET
endstream
