T*
() Tj
T*
(The main screen is simple:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. Paste a long URL.) Tj
T*
(2. Click Shorten.) Tj
T*
(3. Copy the generated short link.) Tj
T*
(4. View recent shortened links.) Tj
